ffi-flite
---------

text to speach
==============

    require 'ffi-flite'

    FFI::Flite.init
    voice = FFI::Flite::Voice.init_kal16
    FFI::Flite.text_to_speech `uptime`, voice, 'play'


flite dependency
================

    git clone git://github.com/optionalgod/flite.git; cd flite
    ./configure --enable-shared --prefix=/usr/local
    make
